# Context Routing Map ([PROJECT_NAME])

Read when: always at session start. Skip when: never.

Start with only `AI_AGENT.md`, `docs/SESSION_BRIEF.md`, `docs/CONTEXT_ROUTING.md`. Pull deeper docs only on triggers.

## Doc Triggers

| Doc | Load when |
|---|---|
| `docs/PROJECT_CANVAS.md` | scope, milestone, or next action unclear |
| `docs/SCENARIO_PLAYBOOK.md` | Level 1/2/3 mode, retrofit, cloud-to-local migration, overnight run |
| `docs/CLOSING_CHECKLIST.md` | final handoff / asks if done |
| `docs/ENGINEERING_PLAYBOOK.md` | commands, tests, CI, validation, feature workflow |
| `docs/TECH_STACK.md` | architecture, dependency, integration boundary |
| `docs/MASTER_TRACEABILITY_TABLE.md` | entrypoint, workflow, side effect, smoke evidence |
| `docs/OPS_SECURITY_RELEASE.md` | deploy, secrets, auth, logging, data, release |
| `docs/TEMPLATE_ADOPTION_WALKTHROUGH.md` | install, retrofit, missing capability, ignored script |
| `CHANGELOG.md` | behavior history or documenting a change |
| `AI_CONTEXT.md` | local reads are insufficient and generated map exists |

## Event Triggers

| Event | Load / Run |
|---|---|
| Choose Level 1/2/3 mode | `docs/SCENARIO_PLAYBOOK.md` |
| Template retrofit | `docs/SCENARIO_PLAYBOOK.md` + `docs/TEMPLATE_ADOPTION_WALKTHROUGH.md` |
| Firebase/cloud-to-local migration | `docs/SCENARIO_PLAYBOOK.md` + `docs/TECH_STACK.md` + `docs/OPS_SECURITY_RELEASE.md` |
| Overnight local-agent run | `docs/SCENARIO_PLAYBOOK.md` + `docs/TEMPLATE_ADOPTION_WALKTHROUGH.md` §5 |
| Version/release/bump | `scripts/bump_version.sh` |
| Merge/predeploy | `scripts/predeploy_full_suite.sh` + `docs/POST_CODING_CHECKS.md` |
| Behavior change lacks docs | `scripts/enforce_doc_updates.sh` |
| Template version bump | `scripts/check_template_drift.sh` + `docs/UPGRADE_GUIDE.md` |
| CI red after DONE | `docs/POST_CODING_CHECKS.md` |
| New entrypoint/workflow | `docs/MASTER_TRACEABILITY_TABLE.md` + `docs/WORKFLOW_TEST_MATRIX.md` |
| New smoke test | `docs/SMOKE_TEST_CATALOG.md` |
| BUGFIX packet | `docs/ENGINEERING_PLAYBOOK.md` regression rule |
| Test modified | `docs/POST_CODING_CHECKS.md` test honesty |
| Existing lean project audit | `docs/TEMPLATE_ADOPTION_WALKTHROUGH.md` §7.5 |
| Session brief has `(not set)` | `docs/GAME_PLAN.md` + `scripts/sync_session_brief.sh` |
| Multi-service or release-prep repo | `docs/TEMPLATE_ADOPTION_WALKTHROUGH.md` §2 |
| Beta/user acceptance | `docs/MASTER_TRACEABILITY_TABLE.md` + `docs/WORKFLOW_TEST_MATRIX.md` |
| Optional/skipped runtime smoke | `scripts/test_smoke.sh` + `docs/ENGINEERING_PLAYBOOK.md` |
| Security docs promise scan | compare ops docs, CI, `scripts/verify.sh` |
| Issue worker packet | `docs/WORKER_TASK_PACKET.md` |
| Worker DONE | `docs/POST_CODING_CHECKS.md` |
| Worker BLOCKED twice | `docs/INVESTIGATOR_PROTOCOL.md` |
| Final handoff / closing checklist | `docs/CLOSING_CHECKLIST.md` |

If event is unlisted and unclear, ask. If more than three deeper docs seem needed before first edit, ask whether task is too broad.
